---
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="problem-section py-20 border-b border-white/10">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        The Problem
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        Today, when an LLM uses a skill, it has to:
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pipeline-diagram flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">1</span>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Read</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">2</span>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Understand</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">3</span>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Reason</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg">
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">4</span>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Execute</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-points max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <div class="grid gap-4 text-text-secondary">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          </svg>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Token waste</strong> — Large models burn tokens parsing long files</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          </svg>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Inconsistency</strong> — Same query, different results each time</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          </svg>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary">Confusion</strong> — Complex skills overwhelm smaller models</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta flex-shrink-0" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
          </svg>
          <span><strong class="text-text-primary">No guarantees</strong> — LLMs interpret text probabilistically</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="solution-section py-20 border-b border-white/10">
  <div class="section-shell">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        The Solution
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-secondary">
        OntoSkills eliminates the reading and understanding phase.
        The reasoner does the heavy lifting.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="pipeline-diagram flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="pipeline-step opacity-40">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg relative">
          <svg class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
            <path d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold line-through">Read</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step opacity-40">
        <div class="step-box border border-white/10 bg-bg-elevated px-6 py-4 rounded-lg relative">
          <svg class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-5 h-5 text-accent-cta" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
            <path d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold line-through">Understand</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-accent-primary/50 bg-accent-primary/10 px-6 py-4 rounded-lg relative">
          <span class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 text-accent-cyan text-xl">~</span>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Reason (OWL)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pipeline-arrow text-text-muted text-2xl">→</div>
      <div class="pipeline-step">
        <div class="step-box border border-accent-success/50 bg-accent-success/10 px-6 py-4 rounded-lg relative">
          <svg class="absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-5 h-5 text-accent-success" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
            <path d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
          </svg>
          <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Execute</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="solution-flow max-w-2xl mx-auto bg-bg-elevated border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 font-mono text-sm">
        <div class="text-text-secondary">Agent: <span class="text-text-primary">"I need to create a PDF"</span></div>
        <div class="text-text-muted pl-4">↓</div>
        <div class="text-accent-cyan">SPARQL: SELECT ?skill WHERE &#123; ?skill oc:resolvesIntent "create_pdf" &#125;</div>
        <div class="text-text-muted pl-4">↓</div>
        <div class="text-accent-success">Result: pdf-generator (deterministic)</div>
        <div class="text-text-muted pl-4">↓</div>
        <div class="text-text-secondary">Agent executes the payload</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-lg text-text-secondary">
      No reading. No guessing. Just <span class="text-accent-cyan">query → execute</span>.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
